{{Quote|Then I would like to send the new fleet into the Seventh Security Zone. I know of several worlds which would welcome even a short visit from a New Republic ship.|[[Gial Ackbar/Legends|Gial Ackbar]]|<ref name="BtS">''[[Before the Storm]]''</ref>}}
The [[Seventh Security Zone]] was a region of [[Realspace/Legends|space]] that was heavily afflicted by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]], including the planet [[Walalla]]. The Seventh was represented in the [[New Republic Senate/Legends|New Republic Senate]] by [[Tig Peramis]].

